_sText:
This is the first map I have ever worked on / made.
So, if you want to comment, please make your comments constructive and if you think that you could make it better, feel free to suggest ideas and you will surely be added to the credits in a (if it exists) second version of this map.
Currently, the map is in beta stage, with the possibility of bugs, so if you find one, please let me know so that it can be fixed asap.

Also, please do not re-upload this anywhere without my permission.
Thanks and please enjoy the map!

Note: The police car and police enforcer models are not mine, they are from GTA:SA I believe and I am not sure who converted them so thanks to the unknown modeller who did those.
